Rating_Title: Maruti Alto 800 Tour Is Awesome Car
Reviews_Description: Maruti Alto 800 tour is an awesome car. Its price is very affordable. It's a very comfortable car.

Rating_Title: Good Experience To Own Alto 800 Tour
Reviews_Description: It's a good experience to own Alto 800 tour car. Sitting is very good & comfortable. Overall the car is superb.
It's an amazing car for my family. The mileage is very good like a bike. Safety is good with amazing features. I think it's a good car for a family.
Zero maintenance car, best in mileage, Smooth and comfortable driving.

Rating_Title: Good Car For The Middle- Class Family
Reviews_Description: This is a nice car for middle-class families and this is the best car at its price segment. its comfort level is good, it comes with good features and the mileage is also good.
It's a good car on a low budget with good mileage.  It's good for middle-class families. I am using it for the office gives great mileage.
